      "properties": {
        "text": "Seedance2.0 asset merge workflow\\n\\nFlow:\\n1. Create two assets from local images\\n2. Merge the two returned asset_id values with RH Seedance2.0素材ID/合并\\n3. Feed the merged asset_ids string into RH Seedance2.0/多模态视频\\n\\nNotes:\\n- The merge node outputs the raw format expected by the Seedance2.0 asset_ids input, for example: asset-xxx, asset-yyy\\n- RH Seedance2.0素材/创建 always uses the fixed internal group group-20260327004931-dvjbj\\n- Multimodal Seedance2.0 will query each asset automatically and route it to imageUrls / videoUrls / audioUrls"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Seedance2.0 asset merge workflow\\n\\nFlow:\\n1. Create two assets from local images\\n2. Merge the two returned asset_id values with RH Seedance2.0素材ID/合并\\n3. Feed the merged asset_ids string into RH Seedance2.0/多模态视频\\n\\nNotes:\\n- The merge node outputs the raw format expected by the Seedance2.0 asset_ids input, for example: asset-xxx, asset-yyy\\n- RH Seedance2.0素材/创建 always uses the fixed internal group group-20260327004931-dvjbj\\n- Multimodal Seedance2.0 will query each asset automatically and route it to imageUrls / videoUrls / audioUrls"
      ],
